      "span_text": "Although the P3 for hard targets starts slightly later than the P3 for easy targets, it also returns back to baseline more rapidly, thus, the small difference in 50% area latency analysis [CITATION_1] ) is nonsignificant [easy targets: mean = 464 msec (SEM = 8) vs. hard targets: mean = 469 msec (SEM = 13); F(1, 10) = 0.55, MSE = 241, p = .476]."
